{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"t